Delicious soup. I made this to use up an abundance of apples and cabbage that I got in my CSA and I wasn't disappointed. The only alteration I made was that I added sausage with the onions at the beginning. I really liked the way that the flavours from the apple topping went together with the rest of the soup. I'll be making this one again!

